                            <comment id="12860218" author="ankur" created="Fri, 23 Apr 2010 11:14:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This script works&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A = LOAD &apos;/tmp&apos; as (a:int, b:chararray, c:int);&lt;br/&gt;
